<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>üöÄ Flask CI/CD DevOps Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
      color: #f8fafc;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 50px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #38bdf8;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p.subtitle {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      width: 400px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      background: #334155;
    }
    .emoji {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    a {
      color: #38bdf8;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .status-light {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #22c55e;
      margin-left: 8px;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite ease-in-out;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 0.8;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1.3);
      }
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    footer strong {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>üöÄ Flask CI/CD DevOps Dashboard</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Monitoring Application Health and Deployment Status</p>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="emoji">‚úÖ</div>
    <h2>App Status</h2>
    <p>Running Successfully <span class="status-light"></span></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Environment</h2>
    <p>development</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Last Build</h2>
    <p>üß± Jenkins Pipeline: Passed</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Docker Image</h2>
    <p>üì¶ tariqueali1731/flask-app:latest</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Kubernetes Status</h2>
    <p>‚ò∏Ô∏è Deployment: Healthy</p>
  </div>

  <p><a href="/api">View JSON API</a></p>

  <footer>Developed by <strong>Tarique Ali</strong></footer>
</body>
</html>
